<h3>Rules for staff profiles</h3>
<ul>
    <li>Must only be used in the main body of the page.</li>
	<li>The biography excerpt should have a character count between 450 and 550 characters.</li>
	<li>If a biography excerpt exceeds 550 characters, and all information included is mandatory, then a follow through biography page must be considered.</li>
	<li>The profile image must be 200 &times; 200 pixels.</li>
	<li>An image must be present if using a link to a full biography.</li>
	<li>The heading link and the full biography link must link to the same page.</li>
	<li>Contact information should be present if available.</li>
</ul>

